                <Header>Contact Information</Header>
                <Paragraph>The website of the United States Senates has a "Suite and Telephone List" (JUN 2021) that is accessible from its "Contacting U.S. Senators" web page. The list is posted in Portable Document Format (PDF) for viewing and downloading. Vice President Kamala D. Harris is the first entry on the list. Phone, 202-224-2424.</Paragraph>
